cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.IR 

The paper focuses on vision-based object detection using deep convolutional neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed framework also involves multi-level analysis and optimization, which are key components of machine learning (cs.AI, cs.LG). Additionally, the paper involves the collection and labeling of a new dataset, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) categories.
